Watch is NOW on iTunes, On Demand, and select theaters 🎭 

Two FBI agents cross paths with Crawford, a Florida cop who's investigating a string of murders that appear to be related. When an undercover sting goes horribly wrong, Crawford soon finds himself in a twisted game of cat and mouse with the killer.

With @meganfox @machinegunkelly @emilehirsch @reallycaitlinxox @oliveabercrombie @lukashaas

node.text: Yooo! The kid (aka me @garrettisthename) just got published on the @wsj about the story of my Monte when it was stolen and it's recovery. I know most of yall know what happened but it's wild to me how 2+ years later this story is still being covered. It wasn't how I wanted me or the car to be known by many but here we are so just rolling with it. I'm thankful for the opportunity to be in such a major publication! Gonna post the link in my bio if yall want to read it! #wallstreetjournal #montecarloss #gbody #comeback

node.text: Does anyone remember this 2006 Ford Super Chief concept? Powered by a Supercharged V10 making 550hp, it ran on gas, ethanol or Hydrogen! And it could do 500 miles on hydrogen power alone while emitting 99% less emissions than gas. Man that is too neat to me! Idk why Hydrogen power wasn't more widely adopted to be honest! That interior is super super modern too! #Ford #superchief #concept #v10 #supercharged
